WEBVTT

00:06:55.449 --> 00:07:00.836
<i>Mary had a little lamb!
Little lamb! Little lamb!</i>

00:07:00.836 --> 00:07:05.336
(Râsete)

00:07:05.336 --> 00:07:08.150
AD: Acest experiment pare complet ridicol.

00:07:08.150 --> 00:07:09.938
(Râsete)

00:07:09.938 --> 00:07:12.283
Ţip la o pungă de chipsuri...

00:07:12.283 --> 00:07:13.834
(Râsete)

00:07:13.834 --> 00:07:18.311
şi proiectam atâta lumină, încât am topit
prima pungă pe care am folosit-o.

00:07:18.311 --> 00:07:20.430
(Râsete)

00:07:20.525 --> 00:07:23.799
Dar oricât de ridicol pare experimentul,

00:07:23.799 --> 00:07:25.587
a fost chiar important,

00:07:25.587 --> 00:07:28.513
pentru că am putut capta acest sunet:

00:07:28.513 --> 00:07:33.225
♪ <i>Mary had a little lamb!
Little lamb! Little lamb!</i> ♪